Tasks:
- Mic input to capture audio from user
- speech to text to convert audio to words
- intent detection to interpret meaning from words (i.e. start a 5 minute timer)
- voice reply to speak back after router executes action (i.e. "it's 42 degrees outside")
- layout zone for screen area reserved for one type of info (i.e. zone for time, weather, calendar, timer, etc) ONLY DISPLAY 
- Full screen mirror display
- weather API to fetch temperature, condition, high/low
- calendar data
- timer backend to start time, for duration, and remaining time (will be displayed by UI)
- state manager (mirror's current knowledge), maintain current weather, active timer, calendar events, and music playing
- media playback for music start/stop and video start/stop
- router for shared integration
